file.name: request_tracker.yaml
file.content:
components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        html_formatted_link: {type: string}
        msg: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp1:
      properties:
        html_formatted_link: {type: string}
        msg: {type: string}
        ticketnumber: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp2:
      properties:
        attachments: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp3:
      properties:
        html_formatted_link: {type: string}
        msg: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp4:
      properties:
        admincc: {type: string}
        cc: {type: string}
        creator: {type: string}
        due: {type: string}
        id: {type: string}
        owner: {type: string}
        priority: {type: string}
        queue: {type: string}
        requestors: {type: string}
        resolved: {type: string}
        starts: {type: string}
        status: {type: string}
        subject: {type: string}
        timeestimated: {type: string}
        timeleft: {type: string}
        timeworked: {type: string}
        told: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes: {}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Request Tracker Request Tracker
  title: Request Tracker Request Tracker
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Request Tracker Add Comment to Ticket
      parameters:
      - description: Optionally test the ability to read a specific ticket
        example: '762'
        in: body
        name: Test Specific Ticket Number
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Comment text to add to the ticket. If your comment contains multiple
          lines, each new line must be preceded by a space (e.g. "line 1\n line 2").
        example: 'Comment message #1'
        in: query
        name: Comment
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: File(s) to attach to the request tracker ticket
        example: Text File.txt
        in: query
        name: File(s)
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Request Tracker Add Comment to Ticket
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Create Request Tracker Ticket
      parameters:
      - description: Ticket queue to create ticket in
        example: General
        in: query
        name: Queue
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Ticket subject
        example: New ticket
        in: query
        name: Ticket Subject
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: New ticket text
        example: My ticket text
        in: query
        name: text
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Request Tracker Create Ticket
  tmp2:
    post:
      description: Search Request Get Attachments
      parameters:
      - description: Ticket ID
        example: '10'
        in: query
        name: Ticket ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp2'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Request Tracker Get Attachments
  tmp3:
    post:
      description: Modify Request Tracker Ticket
      parameters:
      - description: Ticket Number to modify
        example: '223'
        in: body
        name: Ticket Number
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Custom/Other fields to modify. Must be valid JSON format.
        example: '{"CF.{Department}": "Threat Intel", "Title": "Some Title"}'
        in: query
        name: Custom Fields
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp3'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Request Tracker Modify Ticket
  tmp4:
    post:
      description: Search Request Tracker Tickets
      parameters:
      - description: Search Query String
        example: Queue='General'&orderby=+Created
        in: query
        name: Search Query String
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Set this if you would like to ensure you will not receive duplicate
          tickets. Do not add sort order to the query in this case.
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Track State
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp4'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Request Tracker Search Ticket
tags:
- {name: Ticket Management}
